15
00:03:55.348 --> 00:03:56.337
La Mercedes ?

16
00:03:56.449 --> 00:03:59.419
La Lincoln, c'est lourdaud comme bagnole,
je te dis.


17
00:03:59.520 --> 00:04:02.819
